Package fi.tuni.tamk

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidLauncher  
    Box
    Box class creates the boxes used by the Tower Of Life class.
    GameOver
    GameOver class is the gameover screen, that is set when the player loses (TowerOfLife.score == 0).
    Highscore
    Highscore class is the screen with the game highscores.
    Main
    Main class.
    MainMenu
    MainMenu class is the main menu of the game.
    MiniGame
    Minigame class handles the minigame questions and sets different variables in the Tower Of Life class according how player answers the questions.
    Resources
    Resources class is used to initialize all the Textures, Musics, Fonts and Sounds only once to avoid memory build-ups.
    SettingsMenu
    SettingsMenu class is the settings menu of the game.
    TowerOfLife
    Tower Of Life class is the actual main game class.
    Tutorial
    Tutorial class serves as a tutorial for Tower Of Life.
    Util
    Util class contains methods for building Body's for the Boxes.
